lines.text: He said, "Well, if you're pregnant, and you decide to have it, I'm outta here."
Are you avoiding me? Or is it,
Here are your shoes. You can all write me your checks later.

[Looking at the high heels]
Oh, no way! Look, I sprained my ankle and there's no way I'll make it down the aisle in these!
Why don't we all wear flats?
Don't be silly! You all have to match!
